Use case : To deploy Datadog agents on 20k server in large scale enterprise

✅ CMDB CSV file refreshed once per day
✅ 20k+ servers
✅ Goal: deploy / ensure Datadog agent is installed & configured
✅ Run once per day automatically

✅High Level flow : 
Daily CMDB CSV dump
        ↓
CSV → Dynamic Inventory (generated or read)
        ↓
 Ansible Playbook
        ↓
Datadog Agent installed / ensured running
        ↓
Scheduled once per day (cron or AWX)

